    <div class="faq-a" id="how-long-does-it-take-to-see-results-from-scaling-"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>The case studies show a consistent pattern. Months 1-3 produce minimal visible results as Google indexes and evaluates new content. Month 4 is typically the inflection point. Months 6-12 show compounding growth. UserPilot's first 25,000 visitors took 3 years. The next 75,000 took 10 months. The acceleration comes from accumulated indexation, backlinks, and topical authority.</p></div></div>
